Specifically, the following files are adapted from
`python/sglang/srt/function_call/` with minimal modifications (local `Tool`
dataclass in place of SGLang's OpenAI protocol type, strict unknown-tool
handling in place of the SGLang env var, and EdgeVox-native logging):

    base.py          (from base_format_detector.py)
    core_types.py    (from core_types.py)
    utils.py         (from utils.py)
    detectors/hermes.py      (from hermes_detector.py)
    detectors/llama32.py     (from llama32_detector.py)
    detectors/mistral.py     (from mistral_detector.py)
    detectors/pythonic.py    (from pythonic_detector.py)
    detectors/qwen25.py      (from qwen25_detector.py)

